Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.92,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得意思是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Uh, well, I think it means that- -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他们还在外面呢 还没回来呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  They're still out there. They haven't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.72,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-你知道的对吧  -钴队呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  - You know that, right? - Where's Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:45.64,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我只是做本职工作而已  -出什么事了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Look, I'm just doing my job. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是 我们也想知道呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yeah, that's what we're trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.85,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,钴队出什么事了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What happened to Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.81,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不清楚 他们告诉我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I have no idea. They tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.06,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,来把牌子换了 所以我就过来换了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  to change the board, so I, I change the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.98,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,谁让你来换的 凯斯 艾克森\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Who tells you to change it? Keyes, Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.36,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,换回去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,492)} 本剧字幕 由擦枪字幕组 原创译制\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,克莱夫 我们找到一个\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Clive, we've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.85,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.88,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Ah, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.14,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那个可不属于你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  That doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.48,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但你属于我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你跟斯皮夫签过契约\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You're indentured to the Spiffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.40,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不这么认为\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:51.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的标签可不是这么写的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, your tag says otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:58.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿 站住\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  --Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.08,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,放下枪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  --Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.37,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,去小巷\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Take the alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:14.64,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,她在这\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  She's herel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.35,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,她在那边 垃圾处理器 追\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  She's there. The disposal! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.04,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 听到没\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Shut up. Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.46,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,去那边\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,牲口\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,放聪明点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Be a smart girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,鲁比·安买下了索伦的船员 他不会回来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Ruby Ann bought Soren's crew. he's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,克莱夫\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Clive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.47,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你个狡猾的贱人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You slippery bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.15,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,真可惜 现在我都不想速战速决了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  That's a shame. Now I won't even make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我说了停\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I said stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.65,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,有多严重\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.07,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你们这帮混蛋\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.45,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,一辈子都在打仗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  At war your whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,崩溃的时候会意想不到的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  surprised when you break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.12,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-让我帮你  -这里不行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Let me help. -Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.71,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以建议他们把你从前线撤下来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I could recommend that they pull your ass off the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我也可以杀了你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And I could kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.88,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这才对嘛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.30,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,放松 没人在看\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Relax, no one's looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.71,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.18,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-疼吗  -不疼\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -That hurt? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.89,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.06,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-和气些  -别让他们看到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Be nice. - Don't let them see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.94,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,没事 有我在呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It's cool, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.73,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.15,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道自己不可能一辈子都这样的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You know you can't do this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.99,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,斯巴达克战士永不死\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Spartans never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我认真的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.37,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,还有其他事可以做\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  There's other things to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.74,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,其他生活方式\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  other ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.54,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你有考虑过这些吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You ever think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.87,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,考虑什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Think about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:18.29,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不做斯巴达战士的人生\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Life without all this Spartan shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.33,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你是说活的庸庸碌碌\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You mean a life that doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.76,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,路易斯 抱歉 我不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Louis, I'm sorry, I didn't- -
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-没事  -我不是说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -It's all right. - I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.88,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道你们这帮混蛋怎么想的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I know how you assholes think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.34,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我曾经也是你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I was you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你以前很优秀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,曾经是最优秀的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You were the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.39,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,别拍马屁了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Don't blow smoke up my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.52,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但这还真是实话\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.94,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,真希望你能跟我们一起作战\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I wish you were out there with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.77,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是 我以前也这么希望过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yeah, I used to wish that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.28,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么就改想法了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.62,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你不会理解的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.00,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,钴队在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Where's Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.75,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,要喝一杯吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Do you want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.88,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不喝酒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.54,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.92,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那食物呢 你吃东西吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What about food? Do you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.55,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,钴队出什么事了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What happened to Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他们还活着吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Are they still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.10,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,据我所知 斯巴达战士是不会死的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, as far as I know, Spartans never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.48,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,派我们出任务 要不然我就去找能派我们出去的人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Clear us for action, or I'II find somebody who will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.90,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你是在威胁我要越级行事吗 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Are you threatening to go over my head, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.57,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你喜欢等级制度 我尊重这点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You like a hierarchy, I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.49,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但别搞错了 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But make no mistake here, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.41,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,海军情报局才是主脑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  The ONI is running the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.66,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,而我就是海军情报局\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And I am the ONI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:45.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你确定不需要些什么吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You sure I can't get you something, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:49.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那我就直说了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Then allow me to be direct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:53.30,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你对圣所事件的描述已被证实是可疑的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Your account of events on Sanctuary has proven dubious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.84,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们无法证实其真实性\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  We were unable to corroborate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.10,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,去找那个下士 佩雷斯谈啊 她当时也在场\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, talk to that corporal, Perez, she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.06,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我谈过 我们谈了很久\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes, I did. We spoke at length,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.27,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但你坚持发生的这些事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  but these things that you insist happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,星盟精英消灭了陆战队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Covenant Elites wiping out Marines?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.82,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那些陆战队员死了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Those Marines are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你认为他们是怎么死的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What do you think happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.20,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为是星盟将星球玻璃化导致\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I think the Covenant glassed the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为这是场可怕的悲剧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I think it was a terrible tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但事实是 那位下士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But the fact remains, the corporal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.12,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,并没有证实你的说法\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  did not confirm your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.08,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.04,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这话什么意思\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:29.30,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,意思是她完全不记得\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It means she has absolutely no recollection
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.84,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你在圣所遇到的那些事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  of what you say you encountered on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:35.26,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,她在撒谎\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  She's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你设身处地为我想一下 约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Put yourself in my position, John.
