Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,没有我们就赢不了这场战争 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Can't win this war without us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:00.12,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我需要个士官长 我们都需要\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I need Master Chief. We all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:05.67,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但约翰 说到底\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But John, at the end of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.17,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这身衣服换谁穿都行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  he's just a guy in a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:24.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我给你带了吃的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I brought you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.27,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What's wrong?
