Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我跟你说了船准备好我会去找你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I told you I'd come get you when the ship was ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你说今天就能准备好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You said it would be ready today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.33,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是 我知道我说了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yeah, I know what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.42,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们发现个问题\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Um...we found a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.54,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在流体系统管道中发现了个裂缝\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  We found a crack in the stream manifold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.55,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,要多久\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.96,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那艘货船周围有很多碎片\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  There's a lot of debris around that cargo ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.55,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,受到的撞击比我们预想的要多\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  took more hits than we realized
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.76,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-多久  -很难讲\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -How long? -It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.30,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,几天吧 也许更久\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  A couple of days, maybe more.
