Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你应该上楼休息一下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You should go upstairs and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.40,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,索伦绝不会丢下你们任何一个人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Soren never would've left any of you behind.
