Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:17.86,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们被击中 失去了陀螺仪 要么分离 要么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  We got hit, lost the gyro. It was either detach or- -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.28,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你说过了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.41,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-凯斯勒怎么样  -凯斯勒很好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -How's Kessler doing? - Kessler's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.21,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这种事对于孩子来说很难\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  This sort of thing's pretty hard on a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.88,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-索伦没死  -当然没有\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Soren is not dead. - No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.71,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他还活着 明白吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  He's alive, do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,拉埃拉 我们都想找到索伦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Laera, we all wanna find Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.59,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你要知道这不是碎石星唯一一艘飞船\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You know this isn't the only ship on the Rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.26,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这是索伦的飞船\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  This is Soren's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.14,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你们的舰长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.85,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.28,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你耳朵怎么回事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What happened to your ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.07,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我是做错事了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.29,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不是 大人事小孩不懂\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No, it's grown- up stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.12,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,大人事我懂的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I know grown- up stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.42,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我得离开  -为什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  - I have to go. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.88,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 就是得走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Because...I just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.22,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,坏人在找你\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Bad people are looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How do you-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.22,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我都说了大人的事我懂的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I told you I know grown- up things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-你什么都不知道  -你有危险\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  - You don't know anything. You're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.02,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你 你妈\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You, your mom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.73,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,等我爸回来 他就会保护我们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  When my dad comes back, he'll protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.57,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他回不来了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  He's not coming backl
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.28,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.91,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-里兹 我看到你了  -靠\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Riz, I see you. Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.71,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,太慢了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.00,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,已确认目标身份 准备开火\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I have PID on target, taking the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.39,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,游戏结束\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.31,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,跟我说说 是什么感觉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Tell me, what is it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.61,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么  -输的感觉 我不知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  - What? - Losing, I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-你真烦人  -因为我没输过\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -You're insufferable. - Because I've never lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.40,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-是 知道了  -所以对我来说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Yeah, I get it -So for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.57,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个全新的体验\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  it'll be a new experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-士官长 让他闭嘴吧  -再来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Chief, make him stop. We're going again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.37,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-里兹 你上  -收到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Riz, you're up. Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我可以继续 士官长  -我说了里兹来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  - Well, I can go, Chief. I said Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.87,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-士官长  -干嘛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -ChieflWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.00,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧她\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Look at her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.79,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿 还好吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hey, you good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.96,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,很好 士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes, Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.09,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,有什么想说的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Something you wanna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.91,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.37,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-瓦纳克  -我来搞定\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -I got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.18,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,已确认目标身份\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I have PID on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:14.35,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,加油 加油啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.34,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:52.10,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:02.48,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,起来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.36,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-不许放弃  -士官长\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Don't you quit. -Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:10.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-起来  -我做不到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Get upl -I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:12.32,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,别再逼她了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You've gotta stop pushing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.66,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在这训练一晚上了 为什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  we've been out here all night training, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.87,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,因为他们在训练\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Because they re training!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:18.54,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过我在圣所看到了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I told you what I saw on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:20.87,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的敌人就在那里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Our enemy is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.46,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他们越来越近了 我可以证明\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  They're getting close, I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:25.80,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么证明\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How are you gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:27.42,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我要去找钴队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I'm gonna find Cobalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:30.43,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,再一次\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Run it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.06,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:51.07,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,游戏结束了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  The game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:53.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但我们要玩到50分\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But we re playing to 50
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:55.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经50多分了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I got over 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:57.45,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,每轮骰子我都翻倍\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I turned the doubling cube each round,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:24:00.16,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你每次都接受了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  and you accepted every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.12,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,有时候吃点小亏\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Sometimes taking a small loss
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.75,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,比试图获胜要好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  is better than trying to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.12,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:09.63,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,派你来的那个男人是谁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Who's the man who sent you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.13,0:24:13.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How do you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:16.17,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这些可爱的礼物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, these lovely gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,肯定是有人给你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Someone must be giving them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:21.72,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,流个不停呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.76,0:24:23.18,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,跟我说说那个男的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Tell me about the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:27.56,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是 你说过他人很好\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes, you said he's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.60,0:24:28.69,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是 但描述一下他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes, but describe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:30.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我怎么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:31.40,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你要死了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:35.74,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,什么 我是做错什么了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What? Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:37.15,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,看我 看我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Look at me, look at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:41.49,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我好怕  -我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  - I'm scared. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.53,0:24:43.99,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我好害怕  -告诉我他叫什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -I'm very scared. Tell me his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.04,0:24:46.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,告诉我那个男人 他的名字\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Tell me the man, his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.42,0:24:55.71,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这有什么意义呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What's the point in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:05.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,里兹 放松 没事的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Riz, relax. You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.98,0:25:09.39,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不该来这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.48,0:25:11.02,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他是唯一一个能帮到你的人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  He's the only guy that can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.06,0:25:12.65,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.69,0:25:13.61,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,因为他救过我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Cause he's the one who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.69,0:25:18.36,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,听着 我们从增强手术中出来的时候\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Look, when we came outta augmentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.82,0:25:20.91,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己焕然一新\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I felt completely new.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.45,0:25:25.79,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,即使有人开始生病\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Even when people started getting sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.83,0:25:27.87,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我也是不可战胜的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I was invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.91,0:25:30.42,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,几天后\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  After a couple of days,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.50,0:25:32.50,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我视野边缘出现一片黑暗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  there was this darkness at the edge of my vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.25,0:25:36.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我假装它不存在\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I just pretended like it wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.22,0:25:39.55,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但它蔓延\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But it grew...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.68,0:25:42.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,越来越大\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  and it grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.68,0:25:46.01,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我谁都没告诉\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I never told anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.89,0:25:49.64,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你本可以告诉我的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You could have told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.69,0:25:52.56,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-不行  -为什么不行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No, I couldn't. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.61,0:25:55.57,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,因为那样你就会知道我不是你们中的一员\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Cause then you'd know I wasn't one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.61,0:25:58.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道自己只有几天时间\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I knew I only had a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.53,0:25:59.65,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不想当个瞎子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I didn't wanna be somebody going blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.91,0:26:03.41,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我想当斯巴达战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I wanted to be a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.91,0:26:07.54,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,哪怕只那么一小会儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Even if just for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.83,0:26:13.38,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我能看到东西的最后一天\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You know, the last day I could really see anything
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.92,0:26:16.29,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我记得看着你们所有人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I remember looking at all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.26,0:26:19.63,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是如此的骄傲\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  how proud you were
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.09,0:26:23.43,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,如此的美丽\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  how beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.06,0:26:31.69,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,然后一切陷入黑暗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Then it all went dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.90,0:26:35.98,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,保重\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.78,0:26:38.86,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这位是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.90,0:26:42.03,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,一个朋友\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  She's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.07,0:26:43.28,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你好啊 朋友\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hello, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.66,0:26:50.75,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我有点担心约翰\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I am a bit worried about John.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.79,0:26:54.25,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不是士官长的能力 而是这个人市身\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Not Master Chief, but John the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.29,0:26:57.25,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道你们共事很久\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And I know how long you've been togethen
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.30,0:26:59.05,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,知道你在乎他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I know you care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.67,0:27:02.76,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,事实上 我敢说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  In fact, I venture to say
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.80,0:27:05.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你可能比任何人都了解他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  you probably know him better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.72,0:27:08.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-同意吗  -我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Do you agree? - Well, I- -
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.97,0:27:11.22,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我想也许你能帮我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I thought perhaps you might help me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.27,0:27:14.06,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,帮帮他\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.10,0:27:16.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Is that something you could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.48,0:27:19.52,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.90,0:27:25.16,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你有没有看到过任何行为迹象表明\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Have you witnessed any behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.20,0:27:28.53,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,约翰可能会对他的团队构成威胁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  that might indicate John could be a threat to his team
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.62,0:27:31.08,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,甚至可能对自己构成威胁\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  or, God forbid, to himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.25,0:27:38.17,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,没有 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.30,0:27:41.92,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那我就放心了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.01,0:27:51.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得太多了 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I just think it's a lot, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.72,0:27:55.56,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,承载他所承载的 目睹他所目睹的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Carrying everything he carries, seeing everything he's seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.60,0:27:57.85,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,就像他们对他做的那样 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Like what they did to him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.03,0:28:03.65,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我只是有时候在想\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I just wonder sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.70,0:28:08.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他能不能让过去成为过去\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  if he can let the past become the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.83,0:28:13.87,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你担心约翰的精神状态吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Do you have concerns about John's mental state?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.04,0:28:23.26,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不 绝对不是 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No. Absolutely not, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.30,0:28:27.05,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,士官长很可靠 他是最好的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  The chief is solid. He's the best we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.09,0:28:32.01,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我相当理解他看上你什么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, I certainly understand what he sees in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.14,0:28:35.02,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢 长官\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.06,0:28:37.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,只希望他重视你的忠诚\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I only hope he values your loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.31,0:28:42.27,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,就这些了吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Will that be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.32,0:28:43.69,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 解散\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.61,0:28:49.36,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我的门永远为你敞开 凯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  My door is always open, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.00,0:28:56.50,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉艾克森你看到了什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Why didn't you tell Ackerson what you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.54,0:28:57.75,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,抱歉 现在没空\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I'm sorry, this isn't a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.59,0:29:02.17,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,祖母 回屋里去 好吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Abuela, just go back inside, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.21,0:29:04.17,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,大家都在等你呢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Everybody's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.13,0:29:07.47,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-这是谁啊  -他就要走了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  He was just about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.09,0:29:10.76,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你很大只嘛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You are very large.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.80,0:29:13.18,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 女士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.22,0:29:15.18,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他是我同事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  He's someone I work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.22,0:29:18.19,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你跟塔莉亚都在那个星球上吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You were there on that planet with Talia?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.06,0:29:21.86,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.90,0:29:23.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那还站外面干嘛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Why are you standing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.48,0:29:25.23,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,进来一起呀\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Come and join us,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.28,0:29:26.53,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在屋顶上准备了一大堆吃的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  we have a table full of food up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.63,0:29:44.96,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你不是第一个来看我的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You're not the first to come see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:49.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你们这些战士以为伤疤只存在于外部\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You warriors think your scars are on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.18,0:29:50.76,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但其实不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  but they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.10,0:29:59.23,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.15,0:30:07.07,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.28,0:30:10.61,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不过是你的伤痛\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  That's just your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.11,0:30:13.20,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:15.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,让它走吧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.50,0:30:21.25,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的人生是你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Your life is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.29,0:30:22.67,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是属于你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.13,0:30:27.71,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I promise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.71,0:30:28.80,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.38,0:31:08.30,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  A ver,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.34,0:31:10.42,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,招呼客人吃东西啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  make sure our guest gets enough to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.68,0:31:16.34,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你俩是什么情况\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What's the story with you two? Hmm? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.39,0:31:17.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,能安静吃饭吗 拜托了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Can we just eat, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.97,0:31:19.72,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这哥们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Look at this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.77,0:31:21.31,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,肯定特别招女人喜欢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  he must have women climbing all over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.35,0:31:23.23,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,也能是某些男人的菜哦\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Probably some men too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.27,0:31:25.94,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿 管好你自己\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hey, mind your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.98,0:31:28.94,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,拜托 塔莉亚以前没带过人回家\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Come on, Talia never brought anyone home before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.98,0:31:31.07,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他不是我带回来的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I didn't bring him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.11,0:31:33.32,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,是 我觉得我们都应该知道他们有没有\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yeah, and I think we all deserve to know if they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.36,0:31:34.99,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,安东尼奥\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Antonio?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.03,0:31:36.91,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,够了 安东尼奥\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Basta, Antonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.16,0:31:40.54,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.58,0:31:43.41,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿 你的KDR是多少\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hey, what's your KDR?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.21,0:31:47.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,击毙和被击毙率\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Kill- Death ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.63,0:31:49.92,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不是吧兄弟 你不玩斯巴达进攻的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Come on, man, you don't play Spartan Attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.96,0:31:50.96,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不记分的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I don't keep score.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.10,0:32:08.02,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我差点吓尿裤子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Think I almost peed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:13.19,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,都跟你说了 他就是其中一员\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I told you, he's one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.24,0:32:15.20,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我打给贝托\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Oh! I'm calling Beto.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.24,0:32:16.86,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-不行  -是 该打\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  - No. - Yeah, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.95,0:32:18.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了 家里有斯巴达战士来吃饭哎\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What? We have a Spartan at our table.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.78,0:32:20.16,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,当然得打给他了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Of course I'm gonna call him. -
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.87,0:32:23.66,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我想致敬酒词\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I'd like to make a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.62,0:32:29.50,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,敬塔莉亚和她的陆战队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  To Talia and her Marines,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.54,0:32:31.34,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,还有斯巴达战士\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  and the Spartans.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.88,0:32:35.01,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,感谢他们的牺牲\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  We thank God for their sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.22,0:32:37.63,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,敬塔莉亚\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  To Talia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.68,0:32:39.47,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-干杯  -塔莉亚\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Salud. - Talia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.51,0:32:41.81,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,小表妹狠狠教训了那帮星盟垃圾\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Little cousin who kicked some serious Covenant ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.68,0:32:46.18,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿 你怎么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hey, what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.23,0:32:47.64,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 混蛋\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Way to go, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.69,0:32:48.81,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我干什么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.36,0:32:56.03,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,中继站附近通讯中断\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  The comms went down around the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.07,0:32:58.16,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不知道是什么原因造成的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I couldn't figure out what was causing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.66,0:33:05.08,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我当时在扫描波段 然后\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I was scanning the band and.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.37,0:33:08.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,就听到了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.25,0:33:12.25,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,干扰里有声音\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  in the interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.30,0:33:13.63,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你听到什么了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.67,0:33:14.75,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.67,0:33:18.47,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我只知道还有别人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I just knew we weren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.97,0:33:23.64,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道外面有东西\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I knew there was something out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.48,0:33:27.48,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我能感觉到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I could feel it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.52,0:33:28.85,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,兰德也能感觉到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  and Rand could feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.77,0:33:32.61,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我什么都看不到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.90,0:33:36.65,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,现在我战友都牺牲了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And now all my guys are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.07,0:33:39.24,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么解释\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.99,0:33:44.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么解释为什么那东西没杀我\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  How do you explain why that thing didn't kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.83,0:33:46.24,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,因为它本该也把我杀了的啊\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Cause it should've killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.42,0:33:58.47,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是我没告诉艾克森的原因\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  That's why I didn't tell Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.77,0:34:07.35,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他们授予我勋章\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  They gave me a medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.73,0:34:11.35,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我还是不知道由头是什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I still don't know what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.19,0:34:16.57,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,因为活下来吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Surviving?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.74,0:34:21.24,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我只是活下来了而已\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Is that all I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.37,0:34:24.41,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.54,0:34:35.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你听到了一条信息 这种情况还会再次发生\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You heard a message. This will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.55,0:34:42.09,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你每天都会想起这事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You'll think about it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.22,0:34:47.14,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他们的脸会在你最意想不到的时候蹦出来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Their faces pop up when you least expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.35,0:34:50.18,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不会好转\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Doesn't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.02,0:34:55.52,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,只会渐行渐远\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Just gets further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.72,0:35:13.14,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,真奇怪\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.18,0:35:15.76,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,克隆人都说是个很好的男人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  The clones all described a nice man,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.06,0:35:19.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,可你却站在这里\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And yet here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.73,0:35:21.02,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都清楚终有一天我会来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, we both knew I'd be here someday
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.02,0:35:21.81,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都清楚终有一天我会来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, we both knew fd be here someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.53,0:35:28.90,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我父亲在弗农港的花园里有棵\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  There was a pomegranate tree in my father's garden
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.95,0:35:30.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,石榴树\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  in Port Vernon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.07,0:35:35.28,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他花了数年时间培育它\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  He spent years cultivating it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.33,0:35:39.04,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管那棵树并不是安迪密安星球的本土植物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  even though they're not native to Endymion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.08,0:35:42.04,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他曾经每天都在日出前几小时\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And he used to wake me up a couple of hours
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.08,0:35:45.96,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,叫醒我去打理花园\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  before sunrise every day to till the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.00,0:35:49.09,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我为此怨恨过他 觉得这份工作有失我身份\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I resented him for this, I thought the work was beneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.13,0:35:54.72,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我记得有天晚上 有场雷雨\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And I remember one evening there was a lightning storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.76,0:36:00.14,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我偷溜出房间 把他的树点着了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  and I snuck out of my room, and I set his tree on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.18,0:36:02.27,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他从没怀疑过我跟这件事有关系\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  He never suspected I had anything to do with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.11,0:36:08.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我从没告诉过任何人这个故事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I have never told anyone that story
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.78,0:36:14.66,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,然而不知怎么的 那棵树\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  and yet somehow that tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.58,0:36:19.29,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,只有一个人知道这件事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  There's only one person who could know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.33,0:36:23.17,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 如有雷同纯属巧合\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I assure you, any resemblance is pure coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.50,0:36:27.04,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,她在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.13,0:36:30.26,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-科塔娜吗 她很安全  -约翰在哪儿\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Cortana? She's secure. - Where's John?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.30,0:36:32.67,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,先不要操之过急\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Let's not get ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.72,0:36:34.63,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你想从我这里得到什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What is it you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.35,0:36:41.64,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我想给你介绍个人\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  What I want is to introduce you to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.81,0:36:46.56,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这位是朱莉娅\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  This is Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.61,0:36:49.69,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,她将是你的随从\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  She'll be your attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.73,0:36:54.40,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我相信你们二位会很高兴认识对方的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I'm sure you two will enjoy getting to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.53,0:36:58.66,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的树\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Your tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.46,0:37:49.25,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,给我看钴队任务的飞行计划\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Show me the flight plan for Cobalt team's mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.59,0:37:54.26,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,没有与该呼号相关的任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No missions associated with that call sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.13,0:37:58.43,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,给我看所有斯巴达的飞行计划\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Show me all Spartan flight plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.47,0:38:00.97,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,显示斯巴达飞行计划\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Displaying Spartan flight plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.77,0:38:10.65,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你好 科塔娜\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hello, Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.69,0:38:13.40,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你好 艾克森上校\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hello, Colonel Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.44,0:38:15.94,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我为你提供的信息有用吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Did you find the information I provided useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.99,0:38:18.45,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,相当有用 谢谢\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Quite, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.49,0:38:19.95,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,关于哈尔西博士 你还有什么\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Is there anything else you would like to know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.99,0:38:21.99,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,想了解的吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  about Dr. Halsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.03,0:38:24.37,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,没了 可以以后再说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No, we can save that for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.67,0:38:32.29,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我给你的问题有什么进展吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  So, have you made any progress with the problem I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.34,0:38:35.67,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,有的 但这个模拟很复杂\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Yes, but it's a complex simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.72,0:38:37.76,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你能让我访问外部系统\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I could provide you with a more accurate analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.80,0:38:40.01,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我能给你更准确的分析\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  if you could give me access to external systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.09,0:38:41.47,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,恐怕不行\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Well, I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.10,0:38:43.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,但你尽最大努力\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But give it your best shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.97,0:38:45.43,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,即使有误差裕度\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  even with a margin for error,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.48,0:38:47.89,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的预测还是有价值的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  there's value to your projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.94,0:38:50.02,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,根据我掌握的数据\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Based on the data available to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.10,0:38:53.27,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,可能性为97%\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  there's a 97% probability.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.28,0:39:00.03,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,根据你所得到的数据\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  And with the data you've been given,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.11,0:39:02.28,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,有没有什么可行的策略\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  are there any viable strategies you would recommend
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.33,0:39:04.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,可以防止这种结果\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  to prevent that outcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.62,0:39:06.50,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不管采取什么行动\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  AlI of my simulations return the same result
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.54,0:39:09.62,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我所有模拟结果都是一样的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  regardless of any action taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.67,0:39:11.29,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.76,0:39:17.80,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以没什么可做的了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  So there's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.84,0:39:19.93,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以继续模拟\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I can continue to run simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.97,0:39:23.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,不必了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.72,0:39:25.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你要走了吗\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.23,0:39:29.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我会尽可能再来看你的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I'll try and visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.64,0:39:31.52,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你不会的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  But you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.56,0:39:33.90,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你没办法来\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.94,0:39:35.02,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,根据模拟结果\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  According to the simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.07,0:39:36.19,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.74,0:39:40.03,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,只是人类会这么说\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  It's just something people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.08,0:39:50.08,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,交叉搜索通讯中继站\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Crosscheck communications relays.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.16,0:39:53.17,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,有两个正在执行的任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  There are two active missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.25,0:39:57.63,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,子午线中继站 标准船员轮换\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Meridian relay, standard crew rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.67,0:40:00.63,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,未知任务 ε 埃里丹星系\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Unknown mission, Epsilon Eridane system.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.09,0:40:03.34,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,放大\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Zoom in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.35,0:40:11.10,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,任务时间 81小时\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Mission time, 81 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.14,0:40:12.94,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-识别呼号  -无呼号\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  -Identify call sign. - No call sign
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.98,0:40:15.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,与此飞行计划关联\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  associated with this flight plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.48,0:40:18.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他们就没离开过那个星球\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  They never left the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.82,0:40:21.65,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,HV32 这里是致远星飞行B队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Hotel Victor 3- 2, this is Reach Flight Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.70,0:40:24.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你被批准进入长角牛空域 航向249\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  You are cleared for Sector Longhorn, heading 2- 4- 9'er.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.82,0:40:27.03,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,收到 B队 32退出\N{\fs12\1c&HFFDB00&}  Copy that, Bravo. 3- 2 out.
